 unified description between inflation and the $\\Lambda$CDM-like dark\nenergy dominated era can be realized.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 3 Jul 2012 12:04:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 13 Nov 2012 04:45:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-12-14"}
